<i>noun</i>: 실어증 [시러쯩] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>실어증 [시러쯩]</dt><br>
<dd>aphasia</dd><br>
<dd>뇌의 부분적 손상으로 어릴 때부터 익힌 언어의 표현이나 이해에 장애가 생겨 말을 잘 할 수 없거나 못하는 병.</dd><br>
<dd>A disorder with which one cannot speak well or at all, because one's brain is partially damaged and cannot understand the language or remember the expressions learned in the childhood.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>